name: ToriMix
description:
This is a relatively versatile model that can produce artistic and some animated pictures.


The four models used are

  • openjourney (https://civitai.com/models/86/openjourney-aka-midjourney-v4)
  • Dreamlike Diffusion 1.0 (https://civitai.com/models/1274/dreamlike-diffusion-10)
  • seek.art_MEGA v1 (https://civitai.com/models/1315/seekart-mega)
  • waifu diffusion 1.3 penultimate (https://civitai.com/models/44/waifu-diffusion)

I think the anime picture is a little difficult to prompt.
